:: a piece of jade [item] {"position":"325,225","size":"100,100"}
(metadata: 'inventory', 'item')
### A piece of jade
Grandma said it will bring you luck, which hasn't really been working out. You can't remember now how it ended up in your pickup truck. Maybe someday you'll see someone lucky and you can throw it at him.


